                  </tr>

                  <tr>
                    <td>Health Center</td>
                    <td>Read a general <a><%= link_to "overview", about_path %></a> of the H. Rajender Reddy Health Center and all it has to offer. Also see <a><%= link_to "Meet the Staff", meetthestaff_path %></a>.</td>
                  </tr>

                  <tr>
                    <td>Appointments</td>
                    <td>See <a><%= link_to "Medical Appointments", appointments_path %></a> to get started at Health Services and learn how to prepare for your medical appointments, what to expect during and after a clinical visit, and more.</td>
                  </tr>

                  <tr>
                    <td>Required Immunizations</td>
                    <td>All undergraduate and graduate students are covered under the new <a href="/immunizationpolicy.pdf" target="_blank"> UC Merced Campus Immunization Policy</a>. UC Merced has adopted the American College Health Association recommendations for Institutional Pre-Matriculation Immunizations and the recommendation of the Advisory Committee on Immunization Practice of the U.S. Centers for Disease Control. Simply go to the <a href="http://myhealth.ucmerced.edu"><i class="fa fa-h-square fa-fw"></i> myHealth-Messaging</a>  and identify all of your immunizations and the dates they were received.</td>
                  </tr>


                  <tr>
                    <td>Insurance</td>
                    <td>All students are required to have major medical insurance to complement health coverage provided at the Health Center. Learn more about the Student Health Insurance Plan (<a><%= link_to "SHIP", insurance_path %>).</td>
                  </tr>


